    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a nice shine with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with normal driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing some light wear on the driver's seat bolster but no tears or unpleasant odors. Mechanically, the car starts right up and handles well, with all major systems functioning as they should. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
