    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. To ensure long-term mechanical integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled. It retains its factory limited-slip variable M differential and benefits from a refreshed suspension setup featuring Bilstein dampers. This is a driver-focused example with sorted mechanicals and linear power delivery, ready for the street or the track.",
